articles.title: What F1 GPS data reveals about McLaren’s shining Silverstone qualifying - Motorsport.com
articles.description: The last time McLaren sported a part-chrome livery for its home race was 2014. Back then, Jenson Button ran to third in qualifying.
articles.content:
